Date:   Fri Feb 20 01:14:37 2026 +0530

    feat(order): implement concurrency safety and performance optimization
    
    - Concurrency: Pessimistic locking with deterministic lock order in OrderInventoryManagerImpl
    - Scheduler: OrderAutoCancelScheduler for stale order cleanup
    - Performance: HikariCP tuning and open-in-view disabled
    - Pricing: Resolve price from PricingHistory (immutable) with PricingCatalog fallback
    - API: Bulk update results with success/failure tracking (BulkOrderUpdateResultDTO)
    - Helper: OrderTransitionHelper for reusable state transition logic

